{"tid":2378971,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"停車拉咗手擘先入P波既原因","createTime":"2021-01-25T02:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T02:58:59.000Z","uid":363735,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e00190b84a90df7afc69da4ccff7f1523d17b4","tid":2378971,"uid":363735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:15:38.000Z","msg":"我之前喺汽車台另一個thread解釋過停車拉咗手擘先入P波既原因. <br />\n<br />\n迷思：停車係拉咗手擘先入P波，定入完P波先拉咗手擘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2378766/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2378766/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n不過我想再喺呢度開一個新嘅Post 再解釋多一次 .<br />\n<br />\n正確嘅停車程序應該係踩brake將架車極速度減慢到停低. 當架車處於靜止狀態, 應該踩住brake, 與此同時拉手掣/落腳掣, 然後先至鬆開brake. 最後先至入P波, 呢個時候波箱嘅parking pawl 會嘗試扣實連住driving shaft嘅齒輪. 有兩個情況會發生, 一個情況就係 parking pawl入唔中齒輪凹位, 呢個時候手掣後轆brake pad成為成架車唯一嘅制動來源, 萬一手掣失效, 架車會溜前溜後小小, 呢個時候個 parking pawl會插入齒輪凹位, 防止汽車滑行. 第二個情況就係 parking pawl啱啱好食中齒輪凹位, 呢個時候parking pawl 同埋手掣 brake pad成為成架車嘅制動來源, parking pawl承受嘅stress 就會冇咁大.<br />\n<br />\n你可能問點解唔可以入咗p波先落手掣, 原因就係入咗p波先, parking pawl會承受好大嘅mechanical stress. 而parking pawl只不過係波箱裏面一個機械扣, 呢個扣壞咗, 車房佬要拆曬成個波箱落嚟換, 維修成本好大. 但係 brake pad更換起上嚟比起更換波箱入面parking pawl相對嚟講比較平, 所以我個人嚟講會傾向拉咗手掣先然後入p波.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vsRT0NV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvsRT0NV.jpg&h=b5e096b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJDOPGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJDOPGf.jpg&h=22544e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parking_pawl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FParking_pawl&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=35f08ea8\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parking_pawl</a>"},{"pid":"283e27cea6b054c3fa3bb305fb213f1a1f03a217","tid":2378971,"uid":106,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:17:42.000Z","msg":"拉手制先係安全考量，點解會走去睇波箱點work"},{"pid":"598c56db2ac4e61f222f50f6d9a553e2f22167de","tid":2378971,"uid":127929,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:18:50.000Z","msg":"個條友一睇就知傻鳩啦<br />\n<br />\n唔拉手掣走去入p"},{"pid":"79ef570165016fa070d9d3a0327bd6784e5a4f78","tid":2378971,"uid":78819,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:19:00.000Z","msg":"入埋N最好"},{"pid":"5e1317f4b7e496c3fc33c919d3ed262da5d4e279","tid":2378971,"uid":11572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:20:52.000Z","msg":"女人先揸自動波"},{"pid":"f0cfae28e4d7d1d25c48643b33ecd848da94c04c","tid":2378971,"uid":11572,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GWUuy98.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGWUuy98.png&h=8de59360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fq6XH3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFq6XH3M.jpg&h=9a876e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress/http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20070816/large/16ff12p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcache.hkgolden.media%2Fcompress%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20070816%2Flarge%2F16ff12p.jpg&h=d8d629c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63430efaed8c485b74f998b8c6d9d90f73867962","tid":2378971,"uid":363735,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"79ef570165016fa070d9d3a0327bd6784e5a4f78","tid":2378971,"uid":78819,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:19:00.000Z","msg":"入埋N最好"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:25:23.000Z","msg":"而家大部分主流嘅自動波車嘅設計係由Drive推入parking 中間一定會經歷N波,  所以呢個過程已經同你做埋入空波嘅動作 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zW9isvt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzW9isvt.png&h=70465bb7&