波</span>//<br />\n<br />\n唔係要踩住brake先入到波嫁咩,, <br />\n利申: 渣MT"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:42:33.000Z","msg":"多數車入P唔駛踩brake<br />\n由P入R或D先要"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"我仲有個疑問,, <br />\n樓主篇文意思係hand brake先再入P, 有多個brake power個parking pawl 承受個壓力就會無咁大<br />\n咁我踩住brake入P, 個效果又有冇唔同?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:56:09.000Z","msg":"有，如果你喺斜路，拉手制放腳架車點都會un一un，呢一下已經夠卡住個parking pawl，所以應該拉手制n波，un一下，之後先熄匙p波"},{"pid":"9de2452e5c0e84f98278af53aa96129f7588206f","tid":2378971,"uid":122885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8275ef55a6131b53299faeb68e1a1f308eaf86d","tid":2378971,"uid":184956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce8fc0e68691cb57b6a7c154ba65c5987f1b619d","tid":2378971,"uid":122885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c68a3299396cc527b4c55af94e96588313f36f9","tid":2378971,"uid":184956,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:25:58.000Z","msg":"//當架車處於靜止狀態, 應該踩住brake, 與此同時拉手掣/落腳掣, <span class=\"red\">然後先至鬆開brake. 最後先至入P波</span>//<br />\n<br />\n唔係要踩住brake先入到波嫁咩,, <br />\n利申: 渣MT"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:42:33.000Z","msg":"多數車入P唔駛踩brake<br />\n由P入R或D先要"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"我仲有個疑問,, <br />\n樓主篇文意思係hand brake先再入P, 有多個brake power個parking pawl 承受個壓力就會無咁大<br />\n咁我踩住brake入P, 個效果又有冇唔同?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:58:59.000Z","msg":"其實係拉手掣後仲要鬆brake，等架車嘅餘力走埋先再推去P等個parking pawl engage就最好。尤其喺斜路。<br />\n<br />\n如果架車手鬆唔夠實，喺斜路泊車拉咗完就推去P波，一鬆brake嗰下其實架車都會有少少溜後，呢個時候個parking pawl都好大壓力。"},{"pid":"1edc41cbd250cf04bd7840037022db4a8f9cfe4a","tid":2378971,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e0d5b85acc45c1d98098b19fc2e34998fba6d2a","tid":2378971,"uid":119408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63430efaed8c485b74f998b8c6d9d90f73867962","tid":2378971,"uid":363735,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"79ef570165016fa070d9d3a0327bd6784e5a4f78","tid":2378971,"uid":78819,"l